It seems the there are a few data points with multiple species,
countries and impacted sectors. Let's create a new table with only
unique combinations.

\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\NormalTok{scs\_df }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}

    \AttributeTok{Species =}\NormalTok{ inva\_db}\SpecialCharTok{$}\NormalTok{Species,}
